snippet.title: Reality Fighters™ Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Reality Fighters™ launches for the PS Vita today! Create your own personalized fighter, battle with friends online, and make the world your arena. It's time to put yourself in the battle.

http://us.playstation.com/psvita/games-and-media/psv-reality-fighters.html
